# GitHub Personal Access Token used by `pnpm rollup:sync` to fetch each
# submodule's changelog/ and context-v/ via the GitHub Content API.
#
# Either env var works — GITHUB_TOKEN takes precedence if both are set.
# Anonymous mode works (60 req/hr) if you leave both unset; one full sync
# costs ~60–80 calls so you'll wait an hour between syncs without a token.
#
# Quickest way to set this:
#   echo "GITHUB_API_TOKEN=$(gh auth token)" >> splash/.env
#
# This file is git-ignored. Never commit a real token.

GITHUB_API_TOKEN=
